TextEquiv.Unicode: Vt te ruinis opprimat: num debui
Mactare ad aras entis infandæ greges,
Si feriantur in malis tantis Dei,
En culter ecce ſica de ſacris culens,
uæ cupida fodiat gentis Hebrææ latus.
Flammiſque tradam capita ſceler oſæ luis.
Vt hac Latini gaudeant pr æda canes.
